Ophthalmology, University of California San Diego, La Jolla, CA, USA</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Granet%20DB"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">David B Granet</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>1</sup>
</div>
<ul class="d-buttons inline-list">
<li><button class="d-button" aria-controls="aip_a" aria-expanded="false">Author information</button></li>
